              },
              "free_text": [
                " The main sources of the uncertainties for",
                "the thermal neutron cross-section measurement are",
                "due to the detection efficiency, the statistical",
                "error, the thermal neutron shelf-shielding factor,",
                "the decay data of the radioactive isotopes and",
                "Cadmium correction factor.",
                "Also, total uncertainties include:",
                " * Geometry - 0.50%;",
                " * Mass (foil weight) - 0.30%;",
                " * half-life - 0.25%;",
                " * g-factor - 0.05%;",
                " * Abundance - 0.70%."
